name: HorrorMovieQuiz
0:
”Alexa, open Horror Movie Quiz”
”Alexa, start Horror Movie Quiz”
”Alexa, play Horror Movie Quiz”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: horror movie quiz
des:
Alexa will ask you 5 questions about horror movies. Try to answer them all correctly. Simply listen to the question and 4 possible answers. When you know or think you know the answer say the number of the answer to Alexa. Answers need to be one, two, three or four. 

Have fun playing this horror movie quiz!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
